      <abstract>
        <p>We report the case of a 47-year-old homeless male with a massive infestation of
<italic>Pediculus humanus corporis </italic>on his entire body. Dermoscopy helped
to diagnose pediculosis by showing the involvement of scalp, beard and the genital
region in this disease.</p>
      </abstract>
      <kwd-group>
        <kwd>Dermoscopy</kwd>
        <kwd>Lice infestations</kwd>
        <kwd>Pediculus</kwd>
      </kwd-group>
